sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: GetThemes
    C->>A: GetThemes()
    A->>PM: GetThemes()
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(themes/themes.json)
    PA-->>PM: []LifeTheme
    PM-->>A: []LifeTheme
    A->>A: convertObjective() [recursive DTO conversion]
    A-->>C: []LifeTheme (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: CreateTheme
    C->>A: CreateTheme(name, color)
    A->>PM: CreateTheme(name, color)
    PM->>PM: Validate name & color non-empty
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(theme)
    PA->>PA: GetThemes() [read existing]
    PA->>PA: SuggestAbbreviation() [generate ID]
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(themes.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() transaction
    R-->>PA: ITransaction
    PA->>R: tx.Stage(themes.json)
    PA->>R: tx.Commit("Add theme: X")
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM->>PA: GetThemes() [re-read to get generated ID]
    PA-->>PM: []LifeTheme
    PM-->>A: *LifeTheme
    A-->>C: *LifeTheme (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: UpdateTheme
    C->>A: UpdateTheme(theme)
    A->>A: convertObjectiveToAccess() [recursive]
    A->>PM: UpdateTheme(access.LifeTheme)
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(theme)
    PA->>PA: GetThemes() [read existing]
    PA->>PA: ensureThemeIDs() [assign missing IDs]
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(themes.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: DeleteTheme
    C->>A: DeleteTheme(id)
    A->>PM: DeleteTheme(id)
    PM->>PA: DeleteTheme(id)
    PA->>PA: GetThemes() [read existing]
    PA->>PA: Filter out theme by ID
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(themes.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: SuggestThemeAbbreviation
    C->>A: SuggestThemeAbbreviation(name)
    A->>PM: SuggestThemeAbbreviation(name)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PA-->>PM: []LifeTheme
    PM->>PM: access.SuggestAbbreviation(name, themes)
    PM-->>A: string
    A-->>C: string
